extends layout
block content
  .jumbotron
    .text-center
      h1 Code with Us
      h2 Let's learn to code by building projects for nonprofits
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
          h3 Get Connected
          img(src= 'images/connect.svg', alt='Get great references and connections for your reto help you get a job')
          p Join a community of busy, motivated professionals.
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
          h3 Learn JavaScript
          img(src= 'images/learn.svg', alt='Learn to code and learn full stack JavaScript')
          p Work together on Full Stack JavaScript coding challenges.
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
          h3 Build your Portfolio
          img(src= 'images/portfolio.svg', alt='Build a portfolio of apps for nonprofits')
          p Build apps that solve real problems for real people.
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
          h3 Help Nonprofits
          img(src= 'images/nonprofits.svg', alt='Help empower nonprofits with code')
          p Give nonprofits a boost by empowering them with code.
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          if user
            a.btn.btn-block Go to my next challenge
          else
            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-block Start learning to code (it's free)
          a.btn.btn-block My nonprofit needs coding help
      h2 Campers you'll hang out with:
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4
          img(src='images/testimonial-jen.jpg')
          .testimonial-copy Getting back on track with Free Code Camp and committing to a new career in 2015!
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4
          img(src='images/testimonial-tate.jpg')        
          .testimonial-copy Getting back on track with Free Code Camp and committing to a new career in 2015!
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4
          img(src='images/testimonial-cynthia.jpg')        
          .testimonial-copy Getting back on track with Free Code Camp and committing to a new career in 2015!

        h2 Skills you'll learn:
        .text-center.negative-35
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.ion-social-html5
                h2.black-text HTML5
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.ion-social-css3
                h2.black-text CSS3
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.ion-social-javascript
                h2.black-text JavaScript
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.fa.fa-database.font-awesome-padding
                h2.black-text Databases
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.ion-social-chrome
                h2.black-text DevTools
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.ion-social-nodejs
                h2.black-text Node.js
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.ion-social-angular
                h2.black-text Angular.js
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-3
                .landing-skill-icon.ion-ios-loop-strong
                h2.black-text Agile
      h2 Why you should join our community right now:
      ul
        li.ion-code &thinsp; We're thousands of professionals. We all learn to code together.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; We're building projects for dozens of nonprofits.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; Our community is 100% free and open source.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; You'll learn Full Stack JavaScript and become a Software Engineer.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; You'll work through our focused, interactive courses and tutorials.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; You'll learn to code at your own pace, in your browser or on your phone.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; You'll become qualified for thousands of jobs currently going unfilled.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; You can get help in real time from our community chat rooms.
        li.ion-code &thinsp; We all share one common goal: to boost our careers with code.

      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          a.btn.btn-primary Learn to code today (it's free)